{"title":"嫁接","authors":["黄东成"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":2,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫁接"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄东成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新生命嫁接在老树根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老树根勃发了新生命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝头终于绽出芽叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿的星星点点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是老根苏醒了的梦幻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏醒了青春的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向往，追求和欲望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风，不再是老人慵倦的呵欠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱情的色彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳动着，欢跃着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫁接平平仄仄的咏叹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支民族乐队演奏的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现代迪斯科舞曲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘根错节，盘根错节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老根紧紧拥抱黄土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活力不会衰竭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因有水滋润着民族精神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因有氧呼吸着青春气韵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因有太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光合着时间与空间的长距离。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根须，穿过古老的历史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缓缓地伸延，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝叶，萌发新的美学观，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓬蓬勃勃兴起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫁接，绿色的新生代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是新与老的结合，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美的汇集与撷取，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已不是老根原来的枝叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已不是新枝原来的果实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看强劲的绿叶上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渗透着老根的传统，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活力、神韵和气质。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}